text: Stoke Fleming is a village and civil parish on the A379 road and Start Bay, South of Dartmouth in South Hams, Devon, England. In 2001 there were 1,012 people living in Stoke Fleming. Stoke Fleming has a Library and a primary school.http://www.schoolsnet.com/uk-schools/school-details- reviews/devon/stoke-fleming-community-primary-school/16180339/0/211360.html == References == Category:Villages in Devon Category:Civil parishes in Devon Category:South Hams
